{"tid":1825582,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"男子要求法官容許與前妻及其律師進行決鬥而解決法律糾紛","createTime":"2020-01-15T11:49:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T15:42:30.000Z","uid":29188,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b2594f11c89e35334242d594e390299a75a8995e","tid":1825582,"uid":29188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T11:49:17.000Z","msg":"一名堪薩斯州40歲男子David Ostrom要求法官容許他以決鬥方式，與38歲前妻Bridgette Ostrom和她的律師Matthew Hudson解決相關探視、財產的法律糾紛。<br />\n<br />\n他要法官給他12個星期的時間，準備決鬥所需的日本刀。<br />\n<br />\nDavid Ostrom表示，這是為了回應前妻及其律師的無理要求，如前妻不應戰，可由律師代為上場。<br />\n<br />\n法官則表示，由於雙方的動議和回應均存在違規行為，因此他不會在短期內發布決定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2020/jan/14/man-requests-sword-fight-ex-wife-lawyer-settle-legal-dispute\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fus-news%2F2020%2Fjan%2F14%2Fman-requests-sword-fight-ex-wife-lawyer-settle-legal-dispute&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBm58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=69c12dc0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2020/jan/14/man-requests-sword-fight-ex-wife-lawyer-settle-legal-dispute</a>"},{"pid":"3b5aab5968ae9e0f7ce9425c9ed9492faf7640d3","tid":1825582,"uid":50598,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T11:51:24.000Z","msg":"I demand a trial by combat!"},{"pid":"8b1ec1dd0dbfbdb4611fd6000efe8e470b5727f5","tid":1825582,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b5aab5968ae9e0f7ce9425c9ed9492faf7640d3","tid":1825582,"uid":50598,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T11:51:24.000Z","msg":"I demand a trial by combat!"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T11:53:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24ab743e875d73b5aeb3afbfef4ae5db3f56fa80","tid":1825582,"uid":54927,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T11:53:32.000Z","msg":"跟本人類最基本解決方法"},{"pid":"3f9df78c03dc7f0b7c140a471929c03bd904c530","tid":1825582